commit.title: [plugins] Remove Derive plugin.
commit.message:
[plugins] Remove Derive plugin.

There was some discussion about whether this plugin was still
supported or should be moved to an external repository; it also raised
some questions about integration with the STM.

We submit this commit as a testing/RFC, and we also proceed to trim
`Proof_global` a bit as we would eventually like to get rid of it.
